Xi Jinping to the Greater Bay Area Science Forum to the Greater Bay Area to Hexin-Xinhua News Agency, Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, December 11th. On December 11th, the State President Xi Jinping sent a congratulatory letter to the 2021 Dagan District Science Forum.	 Xi Jinping pointed out that today's world has experienced a large change in a century, global scientific and technological innovation has entered a densely active period, and a new round of scientific and technological revolution and industrial change have a profound impact on the global economic structure.	 The Guangdong -Hong Kong -Macao Greater Bay Area shall focus on the strategic positioning of the construction of the International Science and Technology Innovation Center, strive to build a global scientific and technological innovation highland, and promote the development of emerging industries.	 China is willing to work with scientists and international science and technology organizations around the world to closely cooperate with international science and technology exchanges, strengthen research on major scientific issues, promote common scientific and technological cracking, deepen cooperation in key scientific projects, and jointly promote the development of the world's scientific undertakings to better benefit humanity. In 2021, the Greater Bay Area Science Forum opened in Guangzhou City, Guangdong Province, with the theme of "Exploring the Future and Sharing Science".
